  <brief_title>Targeted Internal Radiation Therapy in Advanced HCC Patients.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Prospective Study of Targeted Internal Radiation Therapy in Patients With Advanced Hepatocellular Carcinoma.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
