  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Via clinical diagnosis and confirm it is advanced hepatocellular carcinoma

          2. mRECIST estimation: necrosis region in HCC

          3. Negative iodine allergy test

          4. Liver function ：Child-Pugh A/B

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. reject to attend；

          2. impossible to come to our hospital for physical examination regularly.

          3. Blood clotting function hindrance; 4, Patients with apparent cardiac, pulmonary,
             cerebral and renal dysfunction,which may affect the treatment of liver cancer.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
